{
  "stem": "12413.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Later, not from my brother-- who knew the secret-- but after the war, in a kibbutz I learned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I met a man who was working at the Garibaldi street, cleaning the building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he told me they had committed suicide by taking cyanide.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] When I left the bath house, I went straight to HASAG.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was the ammunition factory. it was a big-- it was almost a town, with 5,000 working people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My brother was working in this place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was working this place because I was hidden in this attic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he was working in this place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I joined him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know if he knew that my parents-- my parents were dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But then he was disappearing [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] every time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were a group of Jews who were praying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then I learned that later, not from him-- from somebody else-- that he was saying Kaddish for my parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The life in HASAG, it was a hard labor camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was harsh, but bearable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was strong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We got our soup, piece of bread; sometimes a piece of margarine-- and sugar, which was unusual.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But because it was a ammunition factory, and they had a big output of ammunition, and they were satisfied with the working Jews, they gave us somehow, special treatment.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But the selection were continuing-- not by the SS-- just by the Meisters, the supervisors who are taking care of the working group.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We, two of us, we are like two hobos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We have friends in this place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We have some relatives-- distant relatives-- who were good off-- good off, in a way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They have money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They have clothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
